{"tid":94062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一黨治港?] 陳永琪：選委不支持林鄭即反中央","createTime":"2017-01-25T02:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T03:23:11.000Z","uid":18074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5cdd08715abf7702ded0081732d24a06df6ff6","tid":94062,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:11:18.000Z","msg":"《信報》及《明報》今天都引述不具名的消息指，據了解，身兼政協常委的工業界（第二）選委陳永棋，昨日在廠商會與特首參選人林鄭月娥的會面上，表明林鄭是最適當及最有能力的特首人選，又稱誰人不支持林鄭，就等於不支持中央。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》政情專欄作者「李先知」又稱，據了解，陳永棋昨日上午與曾俊華會面時，稱與對方相識多時，過往有很多合作接觸等；到下午與林鄭的會面中，已表明自己「一定會提名」林鄭，更當面明言誰人不支持林鄭，是等於反對中央。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/報章引消息-陳永棋稱-選委不支林鄭等於反中央/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%A0%B1%E7%AB%A0%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E9%99%B3%E6%B0%B8%E6%A3%8B%E7%A8%B1-%E9%81%B8%E5%A7%94%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%AD%89%E6%96%BC%E5%8F%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%2F&d=NgsX4dvaM60oeQzAHgI6lHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=24d42e17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%A0%B1%E7%AB%A0%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E9%99%B3%E6%B0%B8%E6%A3%8B%E7%A8%B1-%E9%81%B8%E5%A7%94%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%AD%89%E6%96%BC%E5%8F%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%2F&h=12f0457f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/報章引消息-陳永棋稱-選委不支林鄭等於反中央/</a>"},{"pid":"2b8edb1f82777c409920f540bb07bac76edd0f71","tid":94062,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e1a2a11c3025078505449a730fcad40d19c7f2","tid":94062,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d060eefac96ff7fc92db0ef25c63849bd02229","tid":94062,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T03:0